snippet.textDisplay: Max's fight game has always been predicated on dictating distance, moving into striking range to land combinations, building  momentum, and a huge gas tank. To fight Volkanovski and win, Max will need to change the very fundementals of his fight game completely. Does one really believe that switching stance and going to body is all that will be needed to beat Volko? Do you really believe that one can change their fight dna and still be as effective in such a short period of time.   Max's  team will not be able to match CKB's fight plan and strategy, as they will definitely have new rabbits in their hat to expose . Volkanovski has many other layers to his game that were not on display in this fight. If a rematch happens in OZ say by mid 2020, I feel it wont go as well as Max and team believe.
